about:
PogoSwapp is a crypto currency exchange interface that connects to decentralized finance platforms DeFi using its own POGO token issued on the binance blockchain which is the SMART CHAIN

But also PogoSwapp at the same time an incubator for launching IDO Initial Dex Offering type projectsFor start up companies

POGOSWAPP will allow its users to stack on its platform safely 

As the project evolves, we will integrate several services that will facilitate the task of our users such as the integration of credit cards for cryptocurrency purchases
